                    "body": "I'm OK with Python. I prefer external DSL such as HCL to internal DSL such as Python because external DSL sometimes lacks dynamic functionalities.\r\n\r\nI want to add the following to requirements:\r\n\r\n* Easy to write syntax (e.g.: less code, less magic and so on)",
